<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Montage"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="モンタージュ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="KAF"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="kaf"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="かふ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花譜"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花谱"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Magic"/><amll:meta key="album" value="魔法"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPZ922011626"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1688520974"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1501447574"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="52O0zDxZGzi4rFjXq4VTY4"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="001OF37R2m3h3f"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="334614943"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:21.540"><div begin="21.280" end="3:21.540"><p begin="21.280" end="23.270" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.280" end="21.450">あ</span><span begin="21.450" end="21.570">あ</span><span begin="21.570" end="21.740">もう</span><span begin="21.990" end="22.210">交</span><span begin="22.210" end="22.450">代</span><span begin="22.450" end="22.640">の</span><span begin="22.640" end="22.760">時</span><span begin="22.760" end="23.060">間</span><span begin="23.060" end="23.270">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊啊已经到了交替的时间</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊啊已經到了交替的時間</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah it&apos;s already time to switch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아 이제 교대할 시간이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah c&apos;est déjà l&apos;heure de se relayer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah ya es hora del cambio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah es ist schon Zeit für den Wechsel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah já é hora de trocar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах уже пришло время меняться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah è già ora di darsi il cambio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa mou koutai no jikan sa</span></p><p begin="23.530" end="25.020" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.530" end="23.710">どう</span><span begin="23.710" end="23.790">し</span><span begin="23.790" end="23.990">よう</span><span begin="23.990" end="24.200">も</span><span begin="24.200" end="24.310">な</span><span begin="24.310" end="24.430">い</span><span begin="24.430" end="24.530">く</span><span begin="24.530" end="24.680">ら</span><span begin="24.680" end="24.830">い</span><span begin="24.830" end="25.020">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">到了无可救药的程度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">到了無可救藥的程度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">To the point where it can&apos;t be helped</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어쩔 도리가 없을 정도야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est à n&apos;y rien pouvoir faire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Es tan inevitable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">So sehr dass man nichts machen kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A ponto de não ter o que fazer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">До такой степени что ничего не поделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">A un punto tale che non c&apos;è nulla da fare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushiyou mo nai kurai sa</span></p><p begin="25.300" end="26.780" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.300" end="25.440">我</span><span begin="25.540" end="25.750">慢</span><span begin="25.750" end="25.960">が</span><span begin="25.960" end="26.180">で</span><span begin="26.180" end="26.290">き</span><span begin="26.290" end="26.440">な</span><span begin="26.440" end="26.540">い</span><span begin="26.540" end="26.630">ん</span><span begin="26.630" end="26.780">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">已经无法忍耐了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">已經無法忍耐了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t hold it in</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">참을 수가 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne peux plus le supporter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No lo puedo soportar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich kann es nicht mehr aushalten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu não consigo aguentar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я больше не могу терпеть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non riesco a sopportarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Gaman ga dekinainda</span></p><p begin="27.050" end="30.300" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.050" end="27.290">本</span><span begin="27.290" end="27.520">当</span><span begin="27.520" end="27.690">の</span><span begin="27.690" end="28.060">正</span><span begin="28.060" end="28.390">体</span><span begin="28.390" end="28.540">を</span><span begin="28.780" end="29.150">曝</span><span begin="29.270" end="29.380">け</span><span begin="29.500" end="29.680">出</span><span begin="29.680" end="29.840">し</span><span begin="29.840" end="29.950">た</span><span begin="29.950" end="30.160">い</span><span begin="30.160" end="30.300">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">好想暴露出真正的本来面目</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">好想暴露出真正的本來面目</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to expose my true identity</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">진짜 정체를 드러내고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux révéler ma véritable identité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero revelar mi verdadera identidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte meine wahre Identität enthüllen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero revelar a minha verdadeira identidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хочу раскрыть свою истинную сущность</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio mettere a nudo la mia vera identità</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hontou no shoutai o sarakedashitai yo</span></p><p begin="30.590" end="32.060" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="30.590" end="31.030">暴</span><span begin="31.030" end="31.130">れ</span><span begin="31.230" end="31.280">ち</span><span begin="31.280" end="31.370">ゃ</span><span begin="31.370" end="31.590">い</span><span begin="31.590" end="31.720">た</span><span begin="31.720" end="31.930">い</span><span begin="31.930" end="32.060">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">好想大闹一场</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">好想大鬧一場</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I want to go wild</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">날뛰어버리고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux me déchaîner</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero causar un alboroto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte wild werden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quero me descontrolar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хочу сорваться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio scatenarmi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Abarechaitai yo</span></p><p begin="32.370" end="35.600" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.370" end="32.450">ど</span><span begin="32.450" end="32.570">っ</span><span begin="32.570" end="32.810">ち</span><span begin="32.810" end="33.000">が</span><span begin="33.000" end="33.580">私</span><span begin="33.680" end="33.850">か</span><span begin="34.130" end="34.220">わ</span><span begin="34.320" end="34.570">か</span><span begin="34.570" end="34.670">ら</span><span begin="34.770" end="35.090">な</span><span begin="35.090" end="35.330">い</span><span begin="35.330" end="35.460">ん</span><span begin="35.460" end="35.600">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">连我自己都分不清哪个才是我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">連我自己都分不清哪個才是我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I don&apos;t know which one is me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어느 쪽이 나인지 모르겠어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne sais plus laquelle est moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No sé cuál de las dos soy yo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich weiß nicht welches ich bin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não sei qual de nós sou eu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сама не знаю какая из них я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non so quale sia la vera me</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dotchi ga watashi ka wakaranainda</span></p><p begin="35.900" end="37.450" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.900" end="36.120">友</span><span begin="36.120" end="36.320">達</span><span begin="36.320" end="36.440">に</span><span begin="36.440" end="36.530">は</span><span begin="36.530" end="36.660">言</span><span begin="36.660" end="36.790">え</span><span begin="36.910" end="37.370">な</span><span begin="37.370" end="37.450">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">对朋友也无法诉说</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">對朋友也無法訴說</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t tell my friends</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">친구에겐 말할 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne peux pas le dire à mes amis</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No se lo puedo decir a mis amigos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Kann es Freunden nicht sagen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não posso contar aos meus amigos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Друзьям сказать не могу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non posso dirlo agli amici</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tomodachi ni wa ienai</span></p><p begin="37.610" end="39.110" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.610" end="37.840">先</span><span begin="37.840" end="38.080">生</span><span begin="38.080" end="38.200">に</span><span begin="38.200" end="38.300">も</span><span begin="38.300" end="38.630">内</span><span begin="38.630" end="39.110">緒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">对老师也要保密</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">對老師也要保密</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It&apos;s a secret from the teacher too</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">선생님께도 비밀이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est un secret même pour le professeur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">También es un secreto para el profesor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch vor dem Lehrer geheim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">É segredo até para o professor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">От учителя тоже в секрете</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È un segreto anche per gli insegnanti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sensei ni mo naisho</span></p><p begin="39.430" end="42.640" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="39.430" end="39.590">一</span><span begin="39.590" end="39.870">瞬</span><span begin="39.870" end="40.040">で</span><span begin="40.040" end="40.280">あ</span><span begin="40.280" end="40.410">っ</span><span begin="40.410" end="40.530">と</span><span begin="40.740" end="40.970">言</span><span begin="40.970" end="41.140">わ</span><span begin="41.140" end="41.400">せ</span><span begin="41.400" end="41.640">ら</span><span begin="41.640" end="41.860">れ</span><span begin="41.860" end="42.050">る</span><span begin="42.050" end="42.300">ん</span><span begin="42.300" end="42.490">だ</span><span begin="42.490" end="42.640">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一瞬间就能让人大吃一惊哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一瞬間就能讓人大吃一驚哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can make them gasp in an instant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">순식간에 앗 하고 놀라게 할 수 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je pourrais les laisser sans voix en un instant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Puedo sorprender a todos en un instante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich kann sie in einem Augenblick überraschen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Posso surpreender a todos em um instante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В одно мгновение могу заставить всех ахнуть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Posso farti rimanere a bocca aperta in un istante</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Isshun de atto iwaserarerunda yo</span></p><p begin="42.960" end="44.420" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.960" end="43.130">妄</span><span begin="43.130" end="43.360">想</span><span begin="43.360" end="43.420">じ</span><span begin="43.420" end="43.620">ゃ</span><span begin="43.620" end="43.750">な</span><span begin="43.750" end="43.890">い</span><span begin="43.890" end="43.970">ん</span><span begin="43.970" end="44.180">だ</span><span begin="44.180" end="44.290">っ</span><span begin="44.290" end="44.420">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这可不是妄想</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這可不是妄想</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I&apos;m telling you it&apos;s not a delusion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">망상이 아니라고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n&apos;est pas une illusion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te digo que no es un delirio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es ist keine Wahnvorstellung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Te digo que não é um delírio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Говорю же это не бред</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ti dico che non è un&apos;illusione</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mousou janaindatte</span></p><p begin="44.700" end="46.280" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="44.700" end="44.900">空</span><span begin="44.900" end="45.120">想</span><span begin="45.120" end="45.170">じ</span><span begin="45.170" end="45.360">ゃ</span><span begin="45.360" end="45.480">な</span><span begin="45.480" end="45.650">い</span><span begin="45.650" end="45.720">ん</span><span begin="45.720" end="45.930">だ</span><span begin="45.930" end="46.040">っ</span><span begin="46.040" end="46.280">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这可不是空想</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這可不是空想</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I&apos;m telling you it&apos;s not a fantasy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">공상이 아니라고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n&apos;est pas un fantasme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te digo que no es una fantasía</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es ist keine Fantasie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Te digo que não é uma fantasia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Говорю же это не фантазия</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ti dico che non è una fantasia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuusou janaindatte</span></p><p begin="46.510" end="49.620" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="46.510" end="47.160">私</span><span begin="47.160" end="47.610">本</span><span begin="47.610" end="47.830">当</span><span begin="47.830" end="48.040">は</span><span begin="48.040" end="48.260">宇</span><span begin="48.260" end="48.710">宙</span><span begin="48.710" end="49.120">人</span><span begin="49.120" end="49.360">な</span><span begin="49.360" end="49.620">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">其实我是外星人哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">其實我是外星人哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I am actually an alien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나 사실은 우주인이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En fait je suis une extraterrestre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En realidad soy una extraterrestre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich bin eigentlich ein Alien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Na verdade eu sou uma alienígena</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">На самом деле я инопланетянка</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io in realtà sono un&apos;aliena</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi hontou wa uchuujin na no</span></p><p begin="49.990" end="53.090" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.990" end="50.240">感</span><span begin="50.240" end="50.450">動</span><span begin="50.450" end="51.000">的</span><span begin="51.000" end="51.120">な</span><span begin="51.320" end="51.890">再</span><span begin="51.890" end="52.220">会</span><span begin="52.220" end="52.450">を</span><span begin="52.450" end="52.660">ど</span><span begin="52.660" end="52.870">う</span><span begin="52.870" end="53.090">ぞ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请欣赏令人感动的重逢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請欣賞令人感動的重逢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Please have a moving reunion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">감동적인 재회를 부디</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Voici d&apos;émouvantes retrouvailles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Disfruta de este reencuentro conmovedor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bitte sehr ein bewegendes Wiederse