t">會如其所願地去期盼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Wish to believe it their way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">믿고 싶은 대로 바라는 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Prient comme ils veulent y croire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Desea creerlo a su manera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wünschen es sich so wie sie es glauben wollen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Desejam da forma que querem acreditar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Желают так как им хочется</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Pregano nel modo in cui vogliono credere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinjitai you ni negaunda</span></p><p begin="1:02.130" end="1:03.660" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.130" end="1:02.250">見</span><span begin="1:02.250" end="1:02.360">た</span><span begin="1:02.360" end="1:02.480">い</span><span begin="1:02.480" end="1:02.580">も</span><span begin="1:02.580" end="1:02.680">の</span><span begin="1:02.680" end="1:02.800">だ</span><span begin="1:02.800" end="1:02.890">け</span><span begin="1:02.890" end="1:03.020">を</span><span begin="1:03.020" end="1:03.140">見</span><span begin="1:03.140" end="1:03.260">て</span><span begin="1:03.260" end="1:03.360">る</span><span begin="1:03.360" end="1:03.480">ん</span><span begin="1:03.480" end="1:03.660">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只看着自己想看的东西</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只看著自己想看的東西</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">They only look at what they want to see</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보고 싶은 것만 보고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ils ne voient que ce qu&apos;ils veulent voir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo está viendo lo que quiere ver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sie sehen nur das was sie sehen wollen</span><span ttm:role="x-translati