ml:lang="de">Welchen Teil magst du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">De qual parte você gosta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Какая часть тебе нравится</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quale parte ti piace</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dono bubun ga suki desu ka</span></p><p begin="1:11.180" end="1:14.400" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.180" end="1:11.640">君</span><span begin="1:11.640" end="1:11.760">の</span><span begin="1:11.870" end="1:12.080">目</span><span begin="1:12.080" end="1:12.290">を</span><span begin="1:12.290" end="1:12.950">私</span><span begin="1:12.950" end="1:13.160">と</span><span begin="1:13.160" end="1:13.600">交</span><span begin="1:13.600" end="1:14.020">換</span><span begin="1:14.020" end="1:14.280">し</span><span begin="1:14.280" end="1:14.400">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">把你的眼睛和我交换</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">把你的眼睛和我交換</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Trade your eyes with mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너의 눈을 나와 교환해서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Échange tes yeux avec les miens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Intercambia tus ojos con los míos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Tausche deine Augen mit meinen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Troque os seus olhos com os meus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поменяйся со мной глазами</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Scambia i tuoi occhi con i miei</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi no me o watashi to koukan shite</span></p><p begin="1:14.720" end="1:17.820" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:14.720" end="1:14.940">見</span><span begin="1:14.940" end="1:15.160">え</span><span begin="1:15.160" end="1:15.270">る</span><span begin="1:15.270" end="1:15.510">世</span><span begin="1:15.510" end="1:15.840">界</span><span begin="1:15.840" end="1:16.070">が</span><span begin="1:16.070" end="1:16.710">同</span><span begin="1:16.710" end="1:16.950">じ</span><span begin="1:16.950" end="1:17.390">な</span><span begin="1:17.390" end="1:17.820">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如果看到的世界是一样的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如果看到的世界是一樣的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If the world we see is the same</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보이는 세계가 같다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si le monde que l&apos;on voit est le même</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si el mundo que vemos es el mismo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn die sichtbare Welt die gleiche ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se o mundo que vemos for o mesmo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если мир который мы видим одинаков</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se il mondo che vediamo è lo stesso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mieru sekai ga onnaji nara</span></p><p begin="1:17.820" end="1:21.630" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:17.820" end="1:18.480">私</span><span begin="1:18.480" end="1:18.640">の</span><span begin="1:18.640" end="1:19.130">正</span><span begin="1:19.130" end="1:19.600">体</span><span begin="1:19.600" end="1:19.790">な</span><span begin="1:19.790" end="1:19.910">ん</span><span begin="1:20.010" end="1:20.220">て</span><span begin="1:20.470" end="1:20.540">わ</span><span begin="1:20.650" end="1:20.900">か</span><span begin="1:20.900" end="1:21.130">ら</span><span begin="1:21.130" end="1:21.530">な</span><span begin="1:21.530" end="1:21.630">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那就无法看穿我的真面目</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那就無法看穿我的真面目</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You won&apos;t know my true identity</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 정체 따윈 알 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu ne connaîtras pas ma véritable identité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nunca sabrás mi verdadera identidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wirst du meine wahre Identität nicht erkennen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você não descobrirá a minha verdadeira identidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мою истинную сущность тебе не узнать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non capirai mai la mia vera identità</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi no shoutai nante wakaranai</span></p><p begin="1:35.440" end="1:38.250" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:35.440" end="1:35.670">あ</span><span begin="1:35.670" end="1:35.850">の</span><span begin="1:35.850" end="1:36.310">人</span><span begin="1:36.310" end="1:36.440">は</span><span begin="1:36.540" end="1:36.820">こ</span><span begin="1:36.820" end="1:36.880">う</span><span begin="1:36.880" end="1:37.020">い</span><span begin="1:37.020" end="1:37.400">う</span><span begin="1:37.660" end="1:38.100">人</span><span begin="1:38.100" end="1:38.250">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕说那个人是这样的人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕說那個人是這樣的人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That person is this kind of person</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">저 사람은 이런 사람이고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette personne est comme ci</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esa persona es de tal manera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jene Person ist so eine Person</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aquela pessoa é de tal jeito</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тот человек вот такой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quella persona è fatta così</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ano hito wa kouiu hito de</span></p><p begin="1:38.320" end="1:40.900" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:38.320" end="1:38.560">こ</span><span begin="1:38.560" end="1:38.650">の</span><span begin="1:38.650" end="1:38.970">人</span><span begin="1:38.970" end="1:39.120">は</span><span begin="1:39.410" end="1:39.560">こ</span><span begin="1:39.560" end="1:39.620">う</span><span begin="1:39.620" end="1:39.710">い</span><span begin="1:39.710" end="1:40.050">う</span><span begin="1:40.050" end="1:40.310">性</span><span begin="1:40.410" end="1:40.740">格</span><span begin="1:40.740" end="1:40.900">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这个人是这样的性格</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這個人是這樣的性格</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This person has this kind of personality</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 사람은 이런 성격이고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette personne a tel caractère</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esta persona tiene tal personalidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Diese Person hat so einen Charakter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esta pessoa tem tal personalidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А у этого вот такой характер</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Questa persona ha questo carattere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono hito wa kouiu seikaku de</span></p><p begin="1:41.150" end="1:45.310" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.150" end="1:41.200">じ</span><span begin="1:41.200" end="1:41.370">ゃ</span><span begin="1:41.370" end="1:41.580">あ</span><span begin="1:41.580" end="1:42.510">私</span><span begin="1:42.510" end="1:42.650">の</span><span begin="1:42.940" end="1:43.380">人</span><span begin="1:43.380" end="1:43.770">柄</span><span begin="1:43.770" end="1:43.940">っ</span><span begin="1:43.940" end="1:44.080">て</span><span begin="1:44.280" end="1:44.500">ど</span><span begin="1:44.500" end="1:44.710">ん</span><span begin="1:44.710" end="1:44.970">な</span><span begin="1:44.970" end="1:45.050">の</span><span begin="1:45.050" end="1:45.160">っ</span><span begin="1:45.160" end="1:45.310">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那么我的人品究竟是怎样的呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那麼我的人品究竟是怎樣的呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Then what kind of character do I have</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그럼 내 인품은 어떤 거냐고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors comment est ma personnalité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Entonces si te preguntas cómo es mi carácter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und wie ist dann meine Persönlichkeit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então como é a minha índole</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А если спросить какой характер у меня</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Allora che tipo di personalità ho io</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jaa watashi no hitogara tte donna no tte</span></p><p begin="1:45.350" end="1:47.990" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:45.350" end="1:45.570">実</span><span begin="1:45.670" end="1:46.190">際</span><span begin="1:46.480" end="1:46.580">ど</span><span begin="1:46.580" end="1:46.680">の</span><span begin="1:46.680" end="1:46.810">く</span><span begin="1:46.810" end="1:46.950">ら</span><span begin="1:46.950" end="1:47.120">い</span><span begin="1:47.120" end="1:47.280">知</span><span begin="1:47.280" end="1:47.370">っ</span><span begin="1:47.370" end="1:47.490">て</span><span begin="1:47.490" end="1:47.680">る</span><span begin="1:47.680" end="1:47.800">の</span><span begin="1:47.800" end="1:47.960">だ</span><span begin="1:47.960" end="1:47.990">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">实际上你又了解多少呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">實際上你又瞭解多少呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">How much do you actually know?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">실제론 어느 정도 알고 있는 거야？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En réalité à quel point la connais-tu ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Cuánto sabes en realidad?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie viel weißt du eigentlich?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O quanto você realmente sabe?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Насколько ты вообще его знаешь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In realtà quanto ne sai?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jissai dono kurai shitteru no da?</span></p><p begin="1:48.230" end="1:49.990" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.230" end="1:48.450">誰</span><span begin="1:48.450" end="1:48.570">か</span><span begin="1:48.570" end="1:48.680">ら</span><span begin="1:48.680" end="1:48.760">も</span><span begin="1:48.760" end="1:48.910">よ</span><span begin="1:48.910" end="1:49.000">く</span><span begin="1:49.000" end="1:49.210">思</span><span begin="1:49.210" end="1:49.360">わ</span><span begin="1:49.360" end="1:49.460">れ</span><span begin="1:49.460" end="1:49.560">た</span><span begin="1:49.560" end="1:49.700">い</span><span begin="1:49.700" end="1:49.800">っ</span><span begin="1:49.800" end="1:49.990">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">想要被所有人留下好印象</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">想要被所有人留下好印象</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Wanting to be thought well of by everyone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">누구에게나 좋게 보이고 싶다고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Vouloir être bien perçue par tout le monde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que quiero caerle bien a todos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass ich von allen gut gefunden werden will</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que eu quero ser bem vista por todos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Что я хочу всем нравиться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che voglio essere ben vista da tutti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dare kara mo yoku omowaretai tte</span></p><p begin="1:49.990" end="1:51.450" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:49.990" end="1:50.370">思</span><span begin="1:50.370" end="1:50.470">っ</span><span begin="1:50.470" end="1:50.690">て</span><span begin="1:50.690" end="1:50.880">る</span><span begin="1:50.880" end="1:50.990">の</span><span begin="1:50.990" end="1:51.120">バ</span><span begin="1:51.120" end="1:51.230">レ</span><span begin="1:51.230" end="1:51.350">て</span><span begin="1:51.350" end="1:51.450">る？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这种小心思暴露了吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這種小心思暴露了嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Is it obvious that I think that?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">생각하는 거 들켰어？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu as deviné que c&apos;est ce que je pense ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Se nota que lo pienso?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ist das offensichtlich?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Será que descobriram que eu penso assim?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Заметно ли что я так думаю</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si capisce che lo sto pensando?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Omotteru no bareteru?</span></p><p begin="1:51.780" end="1:53.240" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.780" end="1:51.950">魔</span><span begin="1:51.950" end="1:52.200">法</span><span begin="1:52.200" end="1:52.430">瓶</span><span begin="1:52.430" end="1:52.550">だ</span><span begin="1:52.550" end="1:52.650">っ</span><span begin="1:52.650" end="1:52.730">て</span><span begin="1:52.730" end="1:52.890">知</span><span begin="1:52.890" end="1:52.990">っ</span><span begin="1:52.990" end="1:53.100">て</span><span begin="1:53.100" end="1:53.210">る</span><span begin="1:53.210" end="1:53.240">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你知道保温瓶吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你知道保溫瓶嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Do you know what a thermos is?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보온병이라는 거 알아？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sais-tu ce qu&apos;est une bouteille isotherme ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Sabes lo que es un termo?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weißt du auch von der Thermoskanne?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você sabe o que é uma garrafa térmica?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А знаешь ли ты про термос</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sai cos&apos;è un thermos?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mahoubin datte shitteru?</span></p><p begin="1:53.530" end="1:56.790" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:53.530" end="1:53.970">複</span><span begin="1:53.970" end="1:54.450">雑</span><span begin="1:54.450" end="1:54.620">な</span><span begin="1:54.620" end="1:55.040">程</span><span begin="1:55.040" end="1:55.510">優</span><span begin="1:55.510" end="1:55.760">れ</span><span begin="1:55.760" end="1:55.970">て</span><span begin="1:55.970" end="1:56.190">る</span><span begin="1:56.190" end="1:56.310">と</span><span begin="1:56.310" end="1:56.620">思</span><span begin="1:56.620" end="1:56.790">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">总觉得越是复杂就越是优秀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">總覺得越是複雜就越是優秀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I think the more complex it is the better it is</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">복잡할수록 뛰어나다고 생각해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je pense que plus c&apos;est complexe plus c&apos;est exceptionnel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Creo que cuanto más complejo mejor es</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich denke je komplexer desto besser</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Acho que quanto mais complexa melhor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Думаю чем сложнее тем лучше</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Penso che più sia complesso più sia eccezionale</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fukuzatsu na hodo sugureteru to omou</span></p><p begin="1:57.040" end="2:01.610" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.040" end="1:57.220">そ</span><span begin="1:57.220" end="1:57.290">う</span><span begin="1:57.290" end="1:57.400">い</span><span begin="1:57.400" end="1:57.530">う</span><span begin="1:57.530" end="1:57.980">考</span><span begin="1:57.980" end="1:58.090">え</span><span begin="1:58.090" end="1:58.190">っ</span><span begin="1:58.190" end="1:58.420">て</span><span begin="1:58.420" end="1:59.020">醜</span><span begin="1:59.020" end="1:59.300">い</span><span begin="1:59.300" end="1:59.490">っ</span><span begin="1:59.490" end="1:59.880">て</span><span begin="2:00.190" end="2:00.610">誰</span><span begin="2:00.610" end="2:00.840">か</span><span begin="2:00.840" end="2:01.040">が</span><span begin="2:01.040" end="2:01.190">言</span><span begin="2:01.190" end="2:01.280">っ</span><span begin="2:01.280" end="2:01.520">て</span><span begin="2:01.520" end="2:01.610">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">有人说这样的想法真丑陋</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">有人說這樣的想法真醜陋</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Someone says that kind of thinking is ugly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그런 생각은 추하다고 누군가가 말하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quelqu&apos;un dit que ce genre de pensée est hideuse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Alguien dice que esa forma de pensar es fea</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jemand sagt dass so eine Denkweise hässlich ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Alguém diz que esse tipo de pensamento é feio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кто-то говорит что такие мысли уродливы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Qualcuno dice che un simile pensiero è brutto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Souiu kangae tte minikui tte dareka ga itteru</span></p><p begin="2:01.920" end="2:03.640" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:01.920" end="2:02.060">あ</span><span begin="2:02.060" end="2:02.090">、</span><span begin="2:02.390" end="2:02.540">もう</span><span begin="2:02.540" end="2:02.810">一</span><span begin="2:02.810" end="2:02.940">人</span><span begin="2:02.940" end="2:03.010">の</span><span begin="2:03.010" end="2:03.480">私</span><span begin="2:03.480" end="2:03.640">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 是另一个我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 是另一個我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah, it&apos;s the other me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아, 또 다른 나야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah, c&apos;est l&apos;autre moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah, esa es la otra yo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah das ist mein anderes Ich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah, é o meu outro eu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах это другая я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah c&apos;è un&apos;altra me</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">A, mou hitori no watashi da</span></p><p begin="2:04.120" end="2:07.380" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:04.120" end="2:04.320">規</span><span begin="2:04.320" end="2:04.700">則</span><span begin="2:04.800" end="2:05.130">的</span><span begin="2:05.130" end="2:05.450">に</span><span begin="2:05.450" end="2:05.680">変</span><span begin="2:05.680" end="2:06.020">わ</span><span begin="2:06.020" end="2:06.290">る</span><span begin="2:06.290" end="2:06.760">心</span><span begin="2:06.760" end="2:07.380">情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">规律性变化的心情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">規律性變化的心情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Regularly changing feelings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">규칙적으로 변하는 심정</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Des sentiments qui changent régulièrement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un estado de ánimo que cambia regularmente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die sich regelmäßig ändernde Stimmung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sentimentos que mudam regularmente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Регулярно меняющееся настроение</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sentimenti che cambiano regolarmente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kisokuteki ni kawaru shinjou</span></p><p begin="2:07.640" end="2:10.870" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:07.640" end="2:07.830">本</span><span begin="2:07.830" end="2:08.090">心</span><span begin="2:08.090" end="2:08.350">な</span><span begin="2:08.350" end="2:08.640">ん</span><span begin="2:08.640" end="2:08.960">て</span><span begin="2:08.960" end="2:09.080">絶</span><span begin="2:09.220" end="2:09.570">対</span><span begin="2:09.570" end="2:09.840">に</span><span begin="2:09.840" end="2:10.340">叫</span><span begin="2:10.340" end="2:10.460">べ</span><span begin="2:10.570" end="2:10.760">な</span><span begin="2:10.760" end="2:10.870">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">绝对无法呼喊出真心话</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">絕對無法呼喊出真心話</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can definitely never shout my true feelings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">진심 따윈 절대로 외칠 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne pourrai jamais hurler mes véritables intentions</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nunca podré gritar mis verdaderos sentimientos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Meine wahren Gefühle kann ich niemals hinausschreien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nunca poderei gritar os meus verdadeiros sentimentos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Истинные чувства ни за что не выкрикнуть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non potrò mai urlare i miei veri sentimenti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Honshin nante zettai ni sakebenai</span></p><p begin="2:11.130" end="2:14.320" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:11.130" end="2:11.400">そ</span><span begin="2:11.400" end="2:11.610">れ</span><span begin="2:11.610" end="2:11.750">で</span><span begin="2:11.880" end="2:12.180">も</span><span begin="2:12.180" end="2:12.750">誰</span><span begin="2:12.750" end="2:13.060">か</span><span begin="2:13.060" end="2:13.380">が</span><span begin="2:13.380" end="2:13.500">言</span><span begin="2:13.500" end="2:13.610">っ</span><span begin="2:13.610" end="2:13.860">て</span><span begin="2:13.860" end="2:13.970">る</span><span begin="2:13.970" end="2:14.070">ん</span><span begin="2:14.070" end="2:14.320">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">尽管如此还是有人在说</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">儘管如此還是有人在說</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even so someone is saying it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래도 누군가가 말하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Malgré tout quelqu&apos;un le dit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aun así alguien lo está diciendo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Trotzdem sagt es jemand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo assim alguém está dizendo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но всё же кто-то говорит</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Eppure qualcuno lo sta dicendo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soredemo dareka ga itterunda</span></p><p begin="2:14.730" end="2:17.840" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:14.730" end="2:14.940">本</span><span begin="2:14.940" end="2:15.160">当</span><span begin="2:15.160" end="2:15.290">の</span><span begin="2:15.290" end="2:15.840">私</span><span begin="2:15.840" end="2:16.060">は</span><span begin="2:16.500" end="2:16.720">君</span><span begin="2:16.720" end="2:16.900">と</span><span begin="2:16.900" end="2:17.230">同</span><span begin="2:17.230" end="2:17.350">じ</span><span begin="2:17.350" end="2:17.470">な</span><span begin="2:17.470" end="2:17.570">ん</span><span begin="2:17.570" end="2:17.840">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真正的我和你是一样的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真正的我和你是一樣的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The real me is the same as you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">진짜 나는 너와 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vraie moi est la même que toi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi verdadero yo es igual que tú</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein wahres Ich ist genau wie du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A verdadeira eu é igual a você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Настоящая я такая же как и ты</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La vera me è uguale a te</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hontou no watashi wa kimi to onaji nanda</span></p><p begin="2:18.220" end="2:21.280" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:18.220" end="2:18.670">時</span><span begin="2:18.670" end="2:18.900">た</span><span begin="2:18.900" end="2:19.100">ま</span><span begin="2:19.100" end="2:19.710">笑</span><span begin="2:19.710" end="2:19.800">っ</span><span begin="2:19.800" end="2:20.030">て</span><span begin="2:20.030" end="2:20.470">嘆</span><span begin="2:20.470" end="2:20.690">い</span><span begin="2:20.690" end="2:21.280">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">偶尔欢笑偶尔叹息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">偶爾歡笑偶爾嘆息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Occasionally laughing and lamenting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">때로는 웃고 한탄하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Parfois je ris et je me lamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">A veces riendo y lamentando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Manchmal lachen und klagen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Às vezes rindo e lamentando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Иногда смеюсь иногда горюю</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">A volte rido e mi lamento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tokitama waratte nageite</span></p><p begin="2:21.780" end="2:23.100" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:21.780" end="2:21.900">モ</span><span begin="2:21.900" end="2:22.010">ン</span><span begin="2:22.010" end="2:22.230">ター</span><span begin="2:22.230" end="2:22.270">ジ</span><span begin="2:22.270" end="2:22.340">ュ</span><span begin="2:22.340" end="2:22.550">の</span><span begin="2:22.550" end="2:22.680">か</span><span begin="2:22.680" end="2:22.750">か</span><span begin="2:22.750" end="2:22.890">っ</span><span begin="2:22.890" end="2:23.100">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">被蒙太奇剪辑过的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">被蒙太奇剪輯過的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Covered by a montage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몽타주가 걸린</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Recouverte d&apos;un montage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cubierta de este montaje</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Von der Montage überlagert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sob o efeito de uma montagem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В этой смонтированной мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sottoposta a montaggio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Montaaju no kakatta</span></p><p begin="2:23.100" end="2:24.850" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.100" end="2:23.320">ど</span><span begin="2:23.320" end="2:23.560">の</span><span begin="2:23.560" end="2:23.770">部</span><span begin="2:23.770" end="2:23.980">分</span><span begin="2:23.980" end="2:24.070">が</span><span begin="2:24.070" end="2:24.300">好</span><span begin="2:24.300" end="2:24.410">き</span><span begin="2:24.410" end="2:24.530">で</span><span begin="2:24.530" end="2:24.640">す</span><span begin="2:24.640" end="2:24.850">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你究竟喜欢哪一个部分呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你究竟喜歡哪一個部分呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Which part do you like</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어느 부분을 좋아하나요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quelle partie aimes-tu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Qué parte de mí te gusta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Welchen Teil magst du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">De qual parte você gosta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Какая часть тебе нравится</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quale parte ti piace</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dono bubun ga suki desu ka</span></p><p begin="2:25.290" end="2:28.520" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:25.290" end="2:25.750">君</span><span begin="2:25.750" end="2:25.960">と</span><span begin="2:25.960" end="2:26.500">私</span><span begin="2:26.500" end="2:26.620">の</span><span begin="2:26.620" end="2:27.050">耳</span><span begin="2:27.050" end="2:27.290">を</span><span begin="2:27.290" end="2:27.720">交</span><span begin="2:27.720" end="2:28.140">換</span><span begin="2:28.140" end="2:28.390">し</span><span begin="2:28.390" end="2:28.520">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">把你和我的耳朵交换</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">把你和我的耳朵交換</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Trade your ears and mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너와 내 귀를 교환해서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Échange tes oreilles avec les miennes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Intercambia tus oídos con los míos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Tausche deine und meine Ohren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Troque os seus ouvidos com os meus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поменяйся со мной ушами</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Scambia le tue orecchie con le mie</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi to watashi no mimi o koukan shite</span></p><p begin="2:28.820" end="2:31.890" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:28.820" end="2:29.040">聞</span><span begin="2:29.040" end="2:29.290">こ</span><span begin="2:29.290" end="2:29.400">え</span><span begin="2:29.400" end="2:29.560">る</span><span begin="2:29.560" end="2:29.960">歌</span><span begin="2:29.960" end="2:30.160">が</span><span begin="2:30.160" end="2:30.820">同</span><span begin="2:30.820" end="2:31.060">じ</span><span begin="2:31.060" end="2:31.460">な</span><span begin="2:31.460" end="2:31.890">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如果听到的歌声是一样的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如果聽到的歌聲是一樣的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If the song we hear is the same</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">들리는 노래가 같다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si la chanson que l&apos;on entend est la même</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si la canción que escuchamos es la misma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn das Lied das wir hören das gleiche ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se a música que ouvimos for a mesma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если песня которую мы слышим одинакова</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se la canzone che sentiamo è la stessa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kikoeru uta ga onnaji nara</span></p><p begin="2:31.890" end="2:35.690" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:31.890" end="2:32.570">私</span><span begin="2:32.570" end="2:32.810">の</span><span begin="2:32.810" end="2:33.450">心</span><span begin="2:33.450" end="2:33.680">な</span><span begin="2:33.680" end="2:33.920">ん</span><span begin="2:33.920" end="2:34.140">て</span><span begin="2:34.600" end="2:35.010">届</span><span begin="2:35.010" end="2:35.250">か</span><span begin="2:35.250" end="2:35.610">な</span><span begin="2:35.610" end="2:35.690">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我的心声就无法传达</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我的心聲就無法傳達</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">My heart won&apos;t reach you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 마음 따윈 닿지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mon cœur ne t&apos;atteindra pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi corazón nunca te alcanzará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wird mein Herz dich niemals erreichen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O meu coração não te alcançará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мое сердце до тебя не достучится</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il mio cuore non ti raggiungerà mai</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi no kokoro nante todokanai</span></p><p begin="2:50.000" end="2:51.320" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:50.000" end="2:50.110">モ</span><span begin="2:50.110" end="2:50.240">ン</span><span begin="2:50.240" end="2:50.430">ター</span><span begin="2:50.430" end="2:50.490">ジ</span><span begin="2:50.490" end="2:50.580">ュ</span><span begin="2:50.580" end="2:50.780">の</span><span begin="2:50.780" end="2:50.890">か</span><span begin="2:50.890" end="2:51.000">か</span><span begin="2:51.000" end="2:51.130">っ</span><span begin="2:51.130" end="2:51.320">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">被蒙太奇剪辑过的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">被蒙太奇剪輯過的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Covered by a montage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몽타주가 걸린</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Recouverte d&apos;un montage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cubierta de este montaje</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Von der Montage überlagert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sob o efeito de uma montagem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В этой смонтированной мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sottoposta a montaggio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Montaaju no kakatta</span></p><p begin="2:51.350" end="2:53.100" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:51.350" end="2:51.570">ど</span><span begin="2:51.570" end="2:51.790">の</span><span begin="2:51.790" end="2:51.980">部</span><span begin="2:51.980" end="2:52.210">分</span><span begin="2:52.210" end="2:52.310">が</span><span begin="2:52.310" end="2:52.530">好</span><span begin="2:52.530" end="2:52.640">き</span><span begin="2:52.640" end="2:52.750">で</span><span begin="2:52.750" end="2:52.890">す</span><span begin="2:52.890" end="2:53.100">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你究竟喜欢哪一个部分呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你究竟喜歡哪一個部分呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Which part do you like</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어느 부분을 좋아하나요</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quelle partie aimes-tu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Qué parte de mí te gusta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Welchen Teil magst du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">De qual parte você gosta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Какая часть тебе нравится</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quale parte ti piace</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dono bubun ga suki desu ka</span></p><p begin="2:53.520" end="2:56.750" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:53.520" end="2:54.000">君</span><span begin="2:54.000" end="2:54.200">と</span><span begin="2:54.200" end="2:54.870">私</span><span begin="2:54.870" end="2:54.970">の</span><span begin="2:55.080" end="2:55.510">パー</span><span begin="2:55.510" end="2:55.750">ツ</span><span begin="2:55.750" end="2:55.860">が</span><span begin="2:55.970" end="2:56.160">混</span><span begin="2:56.160" end="2:56.470">ざ</span><span begin="2:56.470" end="2:56.630">っ</span><span begin="2:56.630" end="2:56.750">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你和我的零件混合在一起</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你和我的零件混合在一起</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Mixing your parts and mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너와 내 파츠가 섞여서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tes pièces et les miennes se mélangent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las partes de ti y de mí se mezclan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn sich deine und meine Teile vermischen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se as suas partes e as minhas se misturarem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если твои и мои детали смешаются</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le tue e le mie parti si mescolano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi to watashi no paatsu ga mazatte</span></p><p begin="2:57.000" end="3:00.150" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:57.000" end="2:57.270">信</span><span begin="2:57.270" end="2:57.490">じ</span><span begin="2:57.490" end="2:57.620">た</span><span begin="2:57.620" end="2:57.830">い</span><span begin="2:57.830" end="2:57.950">こ</span><span begin="2:57.950" end="2:58.140">と</span><span begin="2:58.140" end="2:58.380">が</span><span begin="2:58.380" end="2:59.030">同</span><span begin="2:59.030" end="2:59.270">じ</span><span begin="2:59.270" end="2:59.730">な</span><span begin="2:59.730" end="3:00.150">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如果想要相信的事物是一样的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如果想要相信的事物是一樣的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If what we want to believe is the same</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">믿고 싶은 것이 같다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si ce que l&apos;on veut croire est la même chose</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si lo que queremos creer es lo mismo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und wir das gleiche glauben wollen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E se o que queremos acreditar for o mesmo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И если то во что мы хотим верить одинаково</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se le cose in cui vogliamo credere sono le stesse</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinjitai koto ga onnaji nara</span></p><p begin="3:00.150" end="3:03.620" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:00.150" end="3:00.360">い</span><span begin="3:00.360" end="3:00.590">つ</span><span begin="3:00.590" end="3:00.720">か</span><span begin="3:01.040" end="3:01.630">必</span><span begin="3:01.630" end="3:01.710">ず</span><span begin="3:01.870" end="3:02.110">す</span><span begin="3:02.110" end="3:02.240">れ</span><span begin="3:02.340" end="3:02.790">違</span><span begin="3:02.790" end="3:03.000">う</span><span begin="3:03.000" end="3:03.230">は</span><span begin="3:03.230" end="3:03.340">ず</span><span begin="3:03.460" end="3:03.620">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">总有一天注定会擦肩而过</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">總有一天注定會擦肩而過</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Someday we will surely miss each other</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">언젠가 반드시 엇갈릴 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">On finira sûrement par se croiser un jour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Seguro que algún día nos cruzaremos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Werden wir uns sicher irgendwann verfehlen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Algum dia com certeza iremos nos desencontrar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы обязательно когда-нибудь разминемся</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Prima o poi finiremo per incrociarci</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsuka kanarazu surechigau hazu da</span></p><p begin="3:03.860" end="3:05.110" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:03.860" end="3:04.090">そ</span><span begin="3:04.090" end="3:04.350">う</span><span begin="3:04.350" end="3:04.650">で</span><span begin="3:04.650" end="3:04.750">し</span><span begin="3:04.750" end="3:05.000">ょ</span><span begin="3:05.000" end="3:05.110">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是这样吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是這樣吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Isn&apos;t that right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그렇잖아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">N&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Verdad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nicht wahr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não é mesmo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не так ли</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È così vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sou deshou</span></p><p begin="3:05.440" end="3:06.870" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:05.440" end="3:05.660">ねえ</span><span begin="3:05.660" end="3:05.910">そ</span><span begin="3:05.910" end="3:06.130">う</span><span begin="3:06.130" end="3:06.430">で</span><span begin="3:06.430" end="3:06.540">し</span><span begin="3:06.540" end="3:06.790">ょ</span><span begin="3:06.790" end="3:06.870">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐是这样吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">吶是這樣吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hey isn&apos;t that right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">있잖아 그렇잖아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis n&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oye verdad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hey nicht wahr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ei não é mesmo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эй не так ли</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ehi è così vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nee sou deshou</span></p><p begin="3:07.240" end="3:10.450" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:07.240" end="3:07.670">何</span><span begin="3:07.670" end="3:08.100">者</span><span begin="3:08.100" end="3:08.250">で</span><span begin="3:08.350" end="3:08.560">も</span><span begin="3:08.560" end="3:08.790">な</span><span begin="3:08.790" end="3:08.990">い</span><span begin="3:08.990" end="3:09.640">私</span><span begin="3:09.640" end="3:09.880">た</span><span begin="3:09.880" end="3:10.080">ち</span><span begin="3:10.080" end="3:10.450">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">什么都不是的我们</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">什麼都不是的我們</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We who are nobodies</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아무것도 아닌 우리들은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous qui ne sommes personne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nosotros que no somos nadie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir die wir niemand sind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nós que não somos ninguém</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы не являющиеся никем</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Noi che non siamo nessuno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nanimono demo nai watashitachi wa</span></p><p begin="3:10.740" end="3:13.980" itunes:key="L52" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:10.740" end="3:11.180">傷</span><span begin="3:11.180" end="3:11.410">つ</span><span begin="3:11.410" end="3:11.670">け</span><span begin="3:11.670" end="3:11.880">あ</span><span begin="3:11.880" end="3:12.110">っ</span><span begin="3:12.110" end="3:12.260">て</span><span begin="3:12.530" end="3:12.720">混</span><span begin="3:12.720" end="3:12.970">ざ</span><span begin="3:12.970" end="3:13.160">り</span><span begin="3:13.160" end="3:13.430">合</span><span begin="3:13.430" end="3:13.610">っ</span><span begin="3:13.610" end="3:13.980">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">互相伤害着互相交融着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">互相傷害著互相交融著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hurting each other and mixing together</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">서로 상처입히고 뒤섞여서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous nous blessons et nous mélangeons</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hiriéndonos y mezclándonos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verletzen uns gegenseitig und vermischen uns</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nos machucando e nos misturando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Раня друг друга и смешиваясь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ferendoci a vicenda e mescolandoci</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kizutsukeatte mazariatte</span></p><p begin="3:14.300" end="3:21.540" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:14.300" end="3:14.480">い</span><span begin="3:14.480" end="3:14.720">つ</span><span begin="3:14.720" end="3:14.880">か</span><span begin="3:15.170" end="3:15.610">誰</span><span begin="3:15.610" end="3:15.850">か</span><span begin="3:15.850" end="3:16.030">の</span><span begin="3:16.030" end="3:16.470">何</span><span begin="3:16.470" end="3:16.700">か</span><span begin="3:16.700" end="3:16.920">に</span><span begin="3:16.920" end="3:17.130">な</span><span begin="3:17.130" end="3:17.610">れ</span><span begin="3:17.610" end="3:17.820">る</span><span begin="3:17.820" end="3:18.040">か</span><span begin="3:18.040" end="3:21.540">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">因为总有一天能成为某人的某种存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">因為總有一天能成為某人的某種存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because someday we can become someone&apos;s something</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">언젠가 누군가의 무언가가 될 수 있으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car un jour on pourra devenir quelque chose pour quelqu&apos;un</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque algún día podremos ser algo para alguien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil wir irgendwann für jemanden etwas werden können</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque algum dia poderemos ser algo para alguém</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда-нибудь сможем стать для кого-то чем-то</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un giorno potremo diventare qualcosa per qualcuno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsuka dareka no nanika ni nareru kara</span></p></div></body></tt>